claim.claim-text:
1. A bed-side information system comprising:
body information acquiring means for acquiring body information of a patient;
blood purifying means for purifying blood of said patient, said blood purifying means having a blood circuit for circulating the blood;
blood information acquiring means for acquiring blood information obtained from the blood, said blood information acquiring means connecting to said blood circuit; and
display means for displaying said body information and said blood information, said display means connecting to said body information acquiring means and said blood information acquiring means,
wherein said display means predicts said body information and said blood information using a neural network to display a predicted value.
